---
const clientes = [
  { name: "Sabole", logo: "SABOLE" },
  { name: "I AM Care", logo: "I AM CARE" },
  { name: "Rafa Soler Chef", logo: "RAFA SOLER" },
  { name: "Artesaca", logo: "ARTESACA" },
  { name: "Lipi", logo: "LIPI" },
  { name: "Abrego", logo: "ABREGO" },
  { name: "Audreys", logo: "AUDREYS" },
  { name: "Jevole Coffee", logo: "JEVOLE" },
  { name: "Madness Coffee", logo: "MADNESS" }
];
---

<section id="clientes" class="py-20 bg-sumat-beige">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-oddlini text-sumat-navy mb-6">
        Ya confían en nosotros
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-sumat-teal max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Empresas de diferentes sectores que han confiado en nuestras estrategias de marketing
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Carrusel de logos -->
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Carrusel infinito -->
      <div class="flex animate-scroll-x">
        {[...clientes, ...clientes].map((cliente, index) => (
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mx-8 animate-fade-in" style={`animation-delay: ${index * 0.1}s`}>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 min-w-[200px] h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-sumat-navy mb-1">
                  {cliente.logo}
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm text-sumat-teal">
                  {cliente.name}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Indicadores -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mt-8 space-x-2">
      {clientes.slice(0, 5).map((_, index) => (
        <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-sumat-sky rounded-full opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 cursor-pointer"></div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonios -->
    <div class="mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg animate-slide-up">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sumat-navy rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold mr-4">
            RS
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-sumat-navy">Rafa Soler</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-sumat-teal">Chef & Restaurante</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sumat-teal italic">
          "SUMAT transformó nuestra presencia digital. Ahora tenemos más reservas que nunca."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sumat-teal rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold mr-4">
            AC
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-sumat-navy">Ana Clínica</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-sumat-teal">Clínica Dental</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sumat-teal italic">
          "Los resultados en Google Ads superaron nuestras expectativas. ROI increíble."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sumat-sky rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sumat-navy font-semibold mr-4">
            JC
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-sumat-navy">Juan Club</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-sumat-teal">Discoteca</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sumat-teal italic">
          "Nuestras redes sociales ahora generan eventos llenos. Marketing que funciona."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16 animate-fade-in">
      <p class="text-lg text-sumat-teal mb-6">
        ¿Quieres ser el próximo caso de éxito?
      </p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/34600000000?text=Hola%20SUMAT,%20quiero%20ser%20vuestro%20próximo%20caso%20de%20éxito" 
         target="_blank" 
         rel="noopener noreferrer"
         class="inline-flex items-center bg-sumat-navy hover:bg-sumat-teal text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp mr-2"></i>
        Únete a nuestros clientes
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes scroll-x {
    0% { transform: translateX(0); }
    100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }
  
  .animate-scroll-x {
    animation: scroll-x 30s linear infinite;
  }
  
  .animate-scroll-x:hover {
    animation-play-state: paused;
  }
</style>
